g15message
------------------------------------------
A simple message/alert tool for g15daemon and the Logitech G15.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.0.7-1
  libg15daemon_client1-1.9.5.3-1bl3
  libg15render1-1.2-1bl3

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-7
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://g15daemon.sourceforge.io/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/g15daemon/g15message-1.0.0.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack g15message-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./g15message-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/g15message-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/g15message-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(g15message)
  /usr/bin/g15message.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/g15message.README
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/g15message/README

------------------

